Invocation Name: tasty food thoughts
des:
Tasty Food Thoughts helps make you hungry!

Having trouble deciding what to eat?
Tasty Food Thoughts has got a couple ideas.

Simply ask Tasty Food Thoughts for something tasty, and it will tempt you with delicious food items.

If you weren't hungry before, you'll be drooling by the time you finish using this skill!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
